The molecular formula of methyl 2-[3-(methylaminomethyl)cyclobutyl]oxyacetate is C₁₁H₂₀N₂O₄. This formula consists of:

- 11 carbon atoms (C)
- 20 hydrogen atoms (H)
- 2 nitrogen atoms (N)
- 4 oxygen atoms (O)

Adding these up, we get a total of 11 + 20 + 2 + 4 = 37 atoms in methyl 2-[3-(methylaminomethyl)cyclobutyl]oxyacetate.
